<issue num="1463" status="Dup">
<title>[FCD] Inconsistent value assignment for <tt>atomic_bool</tt></title>
<section><sref ref="[atomics.types.integral]"/></section>
<submitter>INCITS</submitter>
<date>25 Aug 2010</date>

<discussion>
<duplicate><iref ref="1462"/></duplicate>
<p><b>Addresses US-157</b></p>

<p>
<tt>atomic_bool</tt> has a <tt>volatile</tt> assignment operator but not a
non-<tt>volatile</tt> operator. The other integral types have both.
</p>
</discussion>

<resolution>
<p>
Add a non-volatile assignment operator to <tt>atomic_bool</tt>.
</p>
</resolution>

</issue>
